<html>
<head>
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="Content-Type" CONTENT="text/html; charset=utf-8">
<link href="css/style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">

<script src="Scripts/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script language="javascript">
    

    function SetLogOutClientTime() {

        var todayDate = new Date();
        var day = todayDate.getDate()
        var month = todayDate.getMonth() + 1
        var year = todayDate.getFullYear()
        var s = "/"
        var mydate = month + s + day + s + year;
        var hour = todayDate.getHours()
        var min = todayDate.getMinutes()
        var sec = todayDate.getSeconds()

        var ts = ":"
        var Clienttime = mydate + " " + hour + ts + min + ts + sec;
        document.getElementById("ClientDateTimeTemp").value = Clienttime;

        document.logoutpage.action = 'logout.asp';
        document.logoutpage.target = '_self';
        document.logoutpage.submit();
    }

    function state_LogOutClientTime() {

        if (xmlhttp.readyState == 4) {
            if (xmlhttp.status == 200) {
                // Dont do anyting
                alert(xmlhttp.responseText);
            }
            else {
                //alert("Problem retrieving XML data:" + xmlhttp.statusText);
            }
        }
    }

    function LogOutNET() {

        var url = document.getElementById("setupUrl").value;

        if (window.XMLHttpRequest) {
            xmlhttp = new XMLHttpRequest();
            xmlhttp.onreadystatechange = state_ChangeLogOutNET;
            xmlhttp.open("GET", url, true);
            xmlhttp.send(null);
            // branch for IE/Windows ActiveX version
        } else if (window.ActiveXObject) {
            xmlhttp = new ActiveXObject("Microsoft.XMLHTTP");
            if (xmlhttp) {
                xmlhttp.onreadystatechange = state_ChangeLogOutNET;
                xmlhttp.open("GET", url, true);
                xmlhttp.send();
            }
        }
    }

    function state_ChangeLogOutNET() {

        if (xmlhttp.readyState == 4) {
            if (xmlhttp.status == 200) {
                LogOutMVC();
            }
            else {
                // alert("Problem retrieving XML data:" + xmlhttp.statusText);
            }
        }
    }

    function LogOutMVC() {

        var url = document.getElementById("reportUrl").value;

        if (window.XMLHttpRequest) {
            xmlhttp = new XMLHttpRequest();
            xmlhttp.onreadystatechange = state_ChangeLogOutMVC;
            xmlhttp.open("GET", url, true);
            xmlhttp.send(null);
            // branch for IE/Windows ActiveX version
        } else if (window.ActiveXObject) {
            xmlhttp = new ActiveXObject("Microsoft.XMLHTTP");
            if (xmlhttp) {
                xmlhttp.onreadystatechange = state_ChangeLogOutMVC;
                xmlhttp.open("GET", url, true);
                xmlhttp.send();
            }
        }
    }

    function state_ChangeLogOutMVC() {

        if (xmlhttp.readyState == 4) {
            if (xmlhttp.status == 200) {
                LogOutQADashb();
            }
            else {
                //  alert("Problem retrieving XML data:" + xmlhttp.statusText);
            }
        }
    }

    function LogOutQADashb() {

        var url = document.getElementById("qadashbUrl").value;

        if (window.XMLHttpRequest) {
            xmlhttp = new XMLHttpRequest();
            xmlhttp.onreadystatechange = state_ChangeLogOutQADashb;
            xmlhttp.open("GET", url, true);
            xmlhttp.send(null);
            // branch for IE/Windows ActiveX version
        } else if (window.ActiveXObject) {
            xmlhttp = new ActiveXObject("Microsoft.XMLHTTP");
            if (xmlhttp) {
                xmlhttp.onreadystatechange = state_ChangeLogOutQADashb;
                xmlhttp.open("GET", url, true);
                xmlhttp.send();
            }
        }
    }

    function state_ChangeLogOutQADashb() {

        if (xmlhttp.readyState == 4) {
            if (xmlhttp.status == 200) {
                if (document.getElementById("OutStatusTwoway").value == "1") {
                    window.location.href = "https://www.google.com/accounts/Logout?continue=https://appengine.google.com/_ah/logout?continue=" + document.getElementById("LogoutFinalURL").value;
                }
                else {
                    window.location.href = document.getElementById("LogoutFinalURL").value;
                }
            }
            else {
                //alert("Problem retrieving XML data:" + xmlhttp.statusText);
            }
        }
    }

</script>
